data.description: Welcome home to Ypsilanti! 3 bedroom 1 bath ranch with full basement and many upgrades. Newly updated bathroom has a waterfall sink, glass shower doors, and new tile (2018). Other updates include: roof (2017), windows (2016), garbage disposal (2020), sump pump (2022), fuse box (2023). One car garage with access door and extra storage space highlight this well-kept home. Basement has workbench and laundry area and could easily be finished for extra living space.
